de.javasoft.synthetica.addons.systemmonitor
Interface Collector

public interface Collector

A collector simply retrieves a value and a maximum value from a data source and returns the values by the provided methods.

The CollectorFactory contains some predefined collectors for CPU-Usage, Heap-Usage, OS-Memory-Usage and more.
